examples.en: He maintains that no child is really bad.
He maintains Islam must adapt to modern society.
The army maintains a missile range in the desert.
She maintains a hectic schedule as a journalist and mother.
He maintains a sense of optimism, despite all that has happened.
She still maintains a close relationship with her college roommate.
The interaction of yin and yang maintains the harmony of the universe.
The hotel maintains traditional standards of elegance, style, and grace.
